I want to have this site be a spot for users to come to both when things arent going well to help them get back on track and when they are doing good and provide them with positive and productive reenforcement (Probaly will put this part in a Readme)


Lvl 1 - Button to generate random words and phrases of encourgement
Lvl 2 - Users can submit their feedback on their mood/issue
Lvl 3 - Use Ai to give users a more personal response
Max Lvl - Allow users to have active dialog with ai $$